&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and stakeholder management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to balance strategic thinking with hands-on execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in iGaming, gaming, tech, or entertainment industries is a strong advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
